OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 28 May to Sat 6 Jun
OL,6,FFine weather and light winds are
OL,7,Flikely to continue for most places as
OL,8,Fhigh pressure expected to remain in
OL,9,Fplace for much of the UK, although
OL,10,Fthere may be a few showers with the
OL,11,Fodd rumble of thunder in the west on
OL,12,FThursday. Temperatures will remain be
OL,13,Fwarm or very warm inland, but it will
OL,14,Ffeel cooler near the coast, especially
OL,15,Fwith an onshore breeze. Heading into
OL,16,FJune, more in the way of cloud is
OL,17,Fpossible, perhaps accompanied by some
OL,18,Frain and showers at times, though
OL,19,Fstill a lot of warm and dry weather in
OL,20,Fbetween.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
