OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1779545470
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 6 Jun to Sat 20 Jun
OL,6,FHigh pressure is more likely to
OL,7,Fprevail across the south and east,
OL,8,Fwith lower pressure further north and
OL,9,Fwest. Rain and showers are still
OL,10,Fpossible at times, mainly across
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland. During
OL,12,Fmid-June, rain and showers may occur
OL,13,Fmore widely for a time. Drier weather
OL,14,Fis expected between any bouts of
OL,15,Fwetter weather - these drier
OL,16,Finterludes will tend to last longer
OL,17,Facross the south and east of England.
OL,18,FTemperatures are most likely to be
OL,19,Fnear or slightly above average
OL,20,Foverall, with some warm or very warm
OL,21,Fweather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
